        comp
        

        public static DenseMatrix comp(SparseCSR m1,
               SparseCSC m2,
               DenseMatrix m3,
               x10.lang.Boolean plus)
        

        Declaration: comp(m1:x10.matrix.sparse.SparseCSR,m2:x10.matrix.sparse.SparseCSC{self.M==m1.N},m3:x10.matrix.DenseMatrix{self.M==m1.M, self.N==m2.N},plus:x10.lang.Boolean): x10.matrix.DenseMatrix{self==m3, m3.M==m1.M, m3.N==m2.N}.

m1's column. This temp space is used when computing the same row of m3.
This process should run faster than the third one (?)

        Declaration: comp1(m1:x10.matrix.sparse.SparseCSR,m2:x10.matrix.sparse.SparseCSC{self.M==m1.N},m3:x10.matrix.DenseMatrix{self.M==m1.M, self.N==m2.N},plus:x10.lang.Boolean): x10.matrix.DenseMatrix{self==m3, m3.M==m1.M, m3.N==m2.N}.
